h1.p: This simple diagram communicates the core requirements for trade: organisations and people to trade with, products and services to buy and sell, a means of transforming inputs into outputs, a financial mapping based on polarity to orchestrate the exchange, your current economic and operational position, and a publishable record of financial performance; then a reliablenetwork for connecting trading partners together and a trusted currency system to pay for each transaction. However, today this is not enough.
